    <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://www.gov.uk/government/publications/business-school-mid-sized-business-msb-collaboration-supporting-growth-in-the-uks-mid-sized-businesses"/>
    <title>Business school/mid-sized business (MSB) collaboration: supporting growth in the UK's mid-sized businesses</title>
    <content type="html">&lt;div class="govspeak"&gt;&lt;p&gt;Summarises findings and recommendations from the business school mid-sized business (MSB) task force set up by BIS in November 2011. While the Task Force has uncovered many examples of effective business school engagement with MSBs, there is much more that both sides can do to foster stronger, more sustainable relationships. The report is a call to action for business schools to proactively engage with MSBs, and for MSBs to improve their own management capability.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</content>
